subscriptionEditor.heading: Subscription Editor
subscriptionsPage.about: Community Supported Agriculture is a concept, which is among other things, trying to connect a consumer directly with a farmer. One method to achieve this, is to subscribe to deliveries of farm produce (subscriptions). Most common is a weekly subscription with handover on agreed pickup point. In general the more deliveries you prepay the lower the price per delivery.
subscriptionsPage.about2: Below you can see farm's subscription offerings, choose a pickup point in Pickup Points section and in case of interest contact the farmer through one of the contacts listed in Farm section.
